        "text": "You can deceive creatures by changing their perception of their allies\u2019 behavior. Each affected creature suspects their allies have changed allegiance, depending on the outcome of their Will save. Regardless of the effects of the saving throw, the creature is then temporarily immune to *pack breaker* for 1 hour.",
